OL,13,FSports Medicine, the new guidance from
OL,14,Fthe Canadian Society for Exercise
OL,15,FPhysiology also "strongly" recommends
OL,16,Fwomen do daily pelvic floor muscle
OL,17,Ftraining to reduce the risk of urinary
OL,18,Fincontinence.
