OL,5,Cweek'
OL,7,FWomen should also try their best to
OL,8,Fdevelop a healthy sleep routine (such
OL,9,Fas avoiding screen time and
OL,10,Fmaintaining a dark, quiet environment
OL,11,Fbefore bed) to support their mental
OL,12,Fhealth.
OL,14,FThe Canadian researchers said:
OL,15,F"Beginning or returning to MVPA
OL,16,F(moderate to vigorous physical
OL,17,Factivity) in the first 12 weeks
OL,18,Ffollowing childbirth, and better
OL,19,Fquality sleep, are associated with
OL,20,Fimproved mental health.
