OL,7,FThe team said returning to running and
OL,8,Fresistance training is generally safe
OL,9,Fonce a woman is healed from their
OL,10,Fbaby's birth, including Caesarean
OL,11,Fsection.
OL,13,FThey added: "It is essential to
OL,14,Facknowledge that infant feeding and
OL,15,Fcare significantly impacts daily life,
OL,16,Fincluding sleep, thus these
OL,17,Frecommendations may not always be
OL,18,Fachievable, and at times specific
OL,19,Frecommendations within this guideline
OL,20,Fwill not align with current
OL,21,Fcircumstances."
