OL,7,FJustine Roberts, founder and chief
OL,8,Fexecutive of Mumsnet, said clear,
OL,9,Fevidence-based guidance on postpartum
OL,10,Fexercise "is long overdue", and said
OL,11,F"it's encouraging to see
OL,12,Frecommendations that prioritise the
OL,13,Fwellbeing of new mothers, even if some
OL,14,Fof them seem wildly optimistic about
OL,15,Fwhat looking after a newborn entails".
OL,17,F"As Mumsnet users will attest,
OL,18,F'developing a healthy sleep routine'
OL,19,Fis much easier said than done.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
